{"tid":2178980,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"相信年底不少年輕人有望輕鬆上樓做業主","createTime":"2020-08-28T19:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T01:26:36.000Z","uid":99883,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"87bf95023f6b7675a0e0403f4fb8dc0e70b6b072","tid":2178980,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lau2-01_oaBgP_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flau2-01_oaBgP_1200x0.png&h=4561c53d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武肺成年冇得去日本，戲又睇少幾個月，我當你一年去三次旅行，每月睇一套戲，全年唔去唔睇戲都買到樓......掛？<br />\n<br />\n如果唔得，建議一人一信問下大劉個死仔包，點解去少幾次都唔得...呀唔係，應該問下係咪d人去哂日本搞到海洋公園冇人去靠政府接濟呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca049cb24793c76c483549cb69538e51c18dab44","tid":2178980,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T21:46:43.000Z","msg":"二世祖教人上樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec48d664b54479973fa45a6bb93f6e579bac4e11","tid":2178980,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T21:51:42.000Z","msg":"辛苦賺左2蚊<br />\n再加父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225ddeda9f1d493ab6a9b3d4a613b285694f8c75","tid":2178980,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec48d664b54479973fa45a6bb93f6e579bac4e11","tid":2178980,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T21:51:42.000Z","msg":"辛苦賺左2蚊<br />\n再加父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T22:03:07.000Z","msg":"如何月入兩蚊致富<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133f91914ee7a43493268c499ca3d047249873e8","tid":2178980,"uid":370688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply